high_descs: walk through the kitchen to face the table with a toaster to the right of the stove
pick up the sharp knife with a gold handle from the table
turn right, walk to face the sink
put the knife into the sink basin, wash knife, pick up the knife
step back to face the cabinets under the sink
open the top left drawer, put knife inside, close the drawer
anns.task_desc: put a washed knife into a drawer

high_descs: Turn around, head to the lettuce on the table on the far side of the room.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table.
Turn around, bring the knife to the sink on the left.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Bring the knife to the drawer left of the sink.
Open the drawer left of the sink and put the cleaned knife in there.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife in the drawer, left if the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table across the room.
Pick up the knife in the very back of the table, behind the toaster.
Turn around and go to the sink, to your left.
Place the knife on the left side of the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the knife, turn the water off, and remove the knife from the sink.
Move over to your left so that you are in front of the drawer under the counter.
Place the knife in the drawer underneath the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the kitchen drawer.
